1.0.name: wordpress/swfobject-reloaded
1.0.description: This plugin allows easy embedding of swf files and better media management for swf files, allowing swf files to have a height, width, and their own minimum flash version. This plugin adds a swfobject shortcode that can be inserted via the "Add media" button while editing a post. SWF files are now also automatically embedded on their respective attachment pages.
